  ---                                                                                                                
  Summary of F1-2 Scope                                                                                              
                                                                                                                     
  What we're building:                                                                                               
  1. Backend: Recommendation engine with deterministic scoring                                                       
    - Domain entities: Horizon, StockScore, RecommendationResult, EvidencePacket                                     
    - Ports: MarketDataProvider, FundamentalsProvider, NewsProvider, SentimentAnalyzer                               
    - Mock adapters for all providers (no real APIs in MVP)                                                          
    - Scoring: 40% technical + 30% fundamental + 30% sentiment                                                       
    - API: POST /analyze, GET /{run_id}, GET /history                                                                
  2. Frontend: Analysis and results pages                                                                            
    - /analyze - Ticker input + horizon selector                                                                     
    - /results/[runId] - Score cards + allocation chart                                                              
    - /history - Past runs list                                                                                      
                                                                                                                     
  Plan constraints enforced:                                                                                         
  - Free: 3 stocks max, 1M horizon only                                                                              
  - Pro: 5 stocks max, all horizons                                                                                  
                                                                                                                     
